Package com.company.commandPattern.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddCommand
    Command create and add new element to collection
    AddIfMaxCommand
    Command create and add new element to collection, if its price is more then u̶n̶i̶v̶e̶r̶s̶i̶t̶y̶ max price
    AverageOfPriceCommand
    Command types average price of all products
    ClearCommand
    Command deletes all elements in collection
    CountByManufactureCostCommand
    Command counts amount of elements which manufacture cost is equals to some number
    CountLessThanManufactureCostCommand
    Command counts amount of elements which manufacture cost is less than some number
    ExecuteScriptCommand
    Command execute user's script
    ExitCommand
    Command stops the program
    HelpCommand
    Command types names of all commands and their clarifications
    InfoCommand
    Command types information about collection
    RemoveByIdCommand
    Command deletes element by id, or types that there are no element with such id
    RemoveGreaterCommand
    Command deletes all elements which price is more than some number
    SaveCommand
    Command saves collection in json file
    ShowCommand
    Collection types all fields of each element
    ShuffleCommand
    Command shuffles collection
    UpdateCommand
    Collection updates fields of element by its id
